version-compare-desc: Show comparison of core component and extension versions between two wikis
version-compare-extension-count-label: Total count of all extensions and skins
version-compare-unique-extension-count-l: Count of extensions and skins only on this wiki
version-compare-same-extension-count-lab: Count of extensions and skins on both wikis
version-compare-url-field-help-1: API URL (ending in api.php) of the first wiki to compare. Will use the current wiki if left blank.
version-compare-url-field-help-2: API URL (ending in api.php) of the second wiki to compare. Will use the current wiki if left blank.
version-compare-ignore-version-field-lab: Ignore version when deciding if extensions/skins match
